      I Build Things<br/>
      <em class="italic">The Right Way</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-[540px] leading-[1.7]">
      Software engineer at Cloudflare, ex-founding engineer at Dyte (YC W'21). I care about shipping products that are thoughtful, well-crafted, and built to last.
