        <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-muted leading-[1.6]">
          I care about shipping products that are well-crafted — good defaults, clean interfaces, honest engineering. I build <a href="https://github.com/roerohan">open source tools</a>, contribute to developer infrastructure, and <a href="https://blog.roerohan.com">write about the process</a>.
