          My background in <a href="https://github.com/roerohan/CTF-Write-ups">CTFs and penetration testing</a> still shapes how I think about systems. Security isn't my day job anymore, but it's always in the back of my mind.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-card-bg border border-card-border rounded-lg p-6 transition-[border-color] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:border-muted-hover card-prose">
